# Tempr - Mobile Music Queue Generation App

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React Native (Expo)
- **Styling**: NativeWind (Tailwind CSS)
- **Backend**: Supabase (database, auth, edge functions)
- **Deployment**: Vercel
- **APIs**: Spotify, OpenWeather, Gemini, Google Calendar, CLIP, OpenL3

## Architecture
- Use TypeScript throughout
- Keep components modular and reusable
- Use react-native-gesture-handler + reanimated for swipe/scroll
- Abstract API calls in /src/services
- Color scheme in src/theme/colors.ts for dynamic theming
- Environment variables for all API keys - never hardcode

## Key Conventions
- ML/AI logic (CLIP, OpenL3, Gemini): add clear comments
- Default to clean, minimal mobile-first UX
- Run `npm test` before committing
